00:17:19.359 --> 00:17:19.839
BRIAN KELLY: Yeah.

00:17:19.839 --> 00:17:21.672
You have to put a value
on your time, right?

00:17:21.672 --> 00:17:24.794
So you know, if your
time is valuable,

00:17:24.794 --> 00:17:28.660
it can be-- there
is risk involved.

00:17:28.660 --> 00:17:30.330
I know a lot of
people buy gift cards.

