and then try to launder it.

00:17:42.360 --> 00:17:45.520
So even though you really
aren't breaking the law,

00:17:45.520 --> 00:17:47.200
accounts can get frozen.

00:17:47.200 --> 00:17:52.020
There's a lot of downside to
it that I frankly-- for me

00:17:52.020 --> 00:17:57.180
and for business owners
out there-- so for all

00:17:57.180 --> 00:17:59.660
of our Google spend and
Facebook advertising,

