00:37:18.220 --> 00:37:19.267
at South Beach Divers.

00:37:19.267 --> 00:37:20.350
BRIAN KELLY: Oh, the one--

00:37:20.350 --> 00:37:20.740
CLIFF REDEKER: Yeah.

00:37:20.740 --> 00:37:21.470
BRIAN KELLY: Yeah, the
one that I went to.

00:37:21.470 --> 00:37:21.950
CLIFF REDEKER: Yeah.

