Yeah.

00:37:22.190 --> 00:37:23.480
It worked out pretty well.

00:37:23.480 --> 00:37:25.577
So I have it,
like, on the ready.

00:37:25.577 --> 00:37:27.910
So the next time I go to the
South Pacific or something,

00:37:27.910 --> 00:37:29.250
I can just hop on in.

00:37:29.250 --> 00:37:30.910
BRIAN KELLY: I
highly recommend it.

00:37:30.910 --> 00:37:33.534
Everyone thinks you're going to
be claustrophobic in breathing.

00:37:33.534 --> 00:37:36.360
And you'll get over it,
and it's totally worth it.

00:37:36.360 --> 00:37:39.150
It is very dangerous, though,
so take it very seriously.

00:37:39.150 --> 00:37:40.880
I almost died once or twice.

00:37:40.880 --> 00:37:42.338
CLIFF REDEKER: Read
the directions.

