I would just say, be flexible.

00:48:19.280 --> 00:48:23.240
If you have time-- or be
flexible on your destination.

00:48:23.240 --> 00:48:27.700
Or you can still
plan in advance.

00:48:27.700 --> 00:48:29.990
It's not all last minute, right?

