sign-up bonus to spend $3,000

00:49:19.570 --> 00:49:21.105
to pay, you know--

00:49:21.105 --> 00:49:21.980
CLIFF REDEKER: Taxes.

00:49:21.980 --> 00:49:22.938
BRIAN KELLY: Tax, yeah.

