00:49:30.180 --> 00:49:31.721
So as much as
manufactured spending's

00:49:31.721 --> 00:49:37.070
about getting it for free, don't
give cash gifts for weddings.

00:49:37.070 --> 00:49:38.860
Use your Amex and buy
an Amex gift card.

00:49:38.860 --> 00:49:42.670
There might be the $5.95 fee.

00:49:42.670 --> 00:49:44.030
Or give gift cards.

00:49:44.030 --> 00:49:46.430
