00:49:49.210 --> 00:49:50.380
store or a supermarket.

00:49:50.380 --> 00:49:51.484
So there are ways.

00:49:51.484 --> 00:49:52.900
I mean, but at the
end of the day,

00:49:52.900 --> 00:49:56.350
